{"type": "article", "id": 3062, "title": "《银河护卫队》的“劲歌金曲”没听够？这里还有 50 首", "description": "《银河护卫队》已在全球狂揽 7.4 亿美元票房，而主角“星爵”那盘《劲歌金曲合辑 / Awesome Mix Vol. 1》也让纵多影迷爱不释手。我们为你挑选了同时代的另外 50 首经典歌曲，你也可以戴上耳机像“星爵”一样边听边跳啦！", "date": "2014-10-25T11:13:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3371, "name": "银河护卫队"}, {"id": 3751, "name": "摇滚乐"}, {"id": 3646, "name": "电影原声"}, {"id": 3752, "name": "劲歌金曲"}], "category": 3, "column": null, "author": 73, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 109, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103156n6Eu370zAvcwIxjd.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">听完了《银河护卫队》里“星爵”爱不释手的那盘《劲歌金曲合辑 / Awesome Mix Vol. 1》，似乎我们都有点儿意犹未尽。由其令人捧腹的是片尾处萌版的树人格鲁特随着 The Jackson 5 的歌曲<em> I Want You Back</em> 跳舞的场景。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103152L7Jdh9a6wmsSqQu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span>（好吧我们来温习一遍）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODAxMTgzNzY0\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span><em> I Want You Back </em>也是<span>《劲歌金曲合辑 / Awesome Mix Vol. 1》中的一首歌，</span></span>这盘来自“星爵”母亲遗物的卡带，受制于介质，A面 B 面加起来总共也就是 12 首歌，而卡带里的那些歌曲来自于诞生了诸多伟大流行摇滚音乐的 1960 年代末至 1980 年代初，这是一个怎样的时代？</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">1960 年代中后期，由于美国黑人运动，种族文化的融合使得布鲁斯、爵士、灵魂乐这些黑人音乐逐渐流入白人世界，深谙商业规则的白人开始操手经营黑人音乐，流行音乐工业初露端倪，并摸索出了自己的行业规则和淳朴的造星模式，黑白文化共同交织的摇滚乐和 R&amp;B 诞生，The Beatles 和 The Rolling Stones 两支英国摇滚乐队对美国流行乐坛进行了洗刷式的“不列颠入侵”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">1970 年代更是过分地繁花锦簇，朋克、华丽摇滚、迪斯科、电子乐这些音乐风格都在这一时期萌生，并抵达巅峰，而经典摇滚乐更是展现了它自己的蓬勃；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">到了 1980 年代初期，年轻小伙儿们开始感受到组一个独立乐队的魅力。流行音乐工业今天的格局，基本上就是在那段时期里定型的，一些对现在的流行音乐产生了重大影响的音乐明星和摇滚乐队，诸如 David Bowie、Kraftwerk、Pink Floyd、The Beach Boys……也多诞生于那时候。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这一时期的劲歌金曲远远不止 12 首，所以“星爵”那盘卡带上面的标签上写着 Vol. 1。我们先为你精心挑选了 50 首歌，一起来感受一下那个生机勃勃的音乐时代吧。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103153bj7d1a6NxX83on0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">01 Simon &amp; Garfunkel - Bridge over Troubled Water</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">02 Roberta Flack - Killing Me Softly with His Song</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">03 Bee Gees - How Can You Mend a Broken Heart</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">04 Stevie Wonder - You Are the Sunshine of My Life</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">05 Billy Joel - Piano Man</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">06 Kraftwerk - The Model</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">07 Rick Springfield - Jessie's Girl</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">08 The Human League - Don't You Want Me</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">09 Lulu - To Sir With Love</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">10 Dizzy - Tommy Roe</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103153SjGDflFwiX12ZVH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">11 Wings - Silly Love Songs</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">12 Peter, Paul &amp; Mary - Leaving on a Jet Plane</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">13 The Doors - Light My Fire</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">14 The Beatles - All You Need Is Love</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">15 Eurythmics - Sweet Dreams (Are Made of This)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">16 Duran Duran - The Reflex</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">17 John Lennon - Imagine</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">18 Deep Purple - Smoke on the Water</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">19 Pink Floyd - Wish You Were Here</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">20 The Sex Pistols - God Save the Queen</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021031534KqvbyrTsu2zBCN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">21 The Archies - Sugar, Sugar</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">22 Marvin Gaye - I Heard It Through the Grapevine</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">23 Shocking Blue - Venus</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">24 The Jackson 5 – ABC</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">25 Blondie - Call Me</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">26 Bob Dylan - Tangled Up In Blue</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">27 The Monkees - Daydream Believer</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">28 Lou Reed - Walk on the Wild Side</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">29 Queen - Bohemian Rhapsody</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">30 Bruce Springsteen - Born to Run</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103154MiuCT27wnWDdXj9A.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"png\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">31 Madonna - Like a Virgin</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">32 Wham! - Everything She Wants</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">33 The Clash - London Calling</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">34 Michael Jackson - Beat It</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">35 The Kinks – Lola</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">36 The Ramones - I Wanna Be Sedated</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">37 The Velvet Underground - Rock &amp; Roll</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">38 Aerosmith - Dream On</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">39 The Beach Boys - Good Vibrations</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">40 Percy Sledge - When a Man Loves a Woman</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103155X4yWMf15bxICu3PA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.990625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">41 The Beatles - Hey Jude</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">42 Eric Clapton - I Shot the Sheriff</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">43 ABBA - Dancing Queen</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">44 Eagles - Hotel California</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">45 Donna Summer - Bad Girls</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">46 Air Supply - The One That You Love</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">47 Michael Jackson - Billie Jean</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">48 Leo Sayer - You Make Me Feel Like Dancing</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">49 The Police - Every Breath You Take</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">50 David Bowie – Heroes</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><br>\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><strong>关于作者</strong><br>\r\n朴九月，经年累月的文字作者和互联网民工，曾经并一直致力于传播欧美青年文化，对能够催生出力量的音乐、文学、影视作品怀有最诚挚的热爱，并且是这些力量的忠实记录者和传播者，目前在研究东南亚、宗教、建筑、食品健康和世界主义。<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</